thm___）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260503/1127661434101174272105937.jpeg/UFbwLpyyzPQtwpTwzUe3i4NZAG-W0K4k_ZHF-_2Rxfs\" alt=\"鄧凱文身材好好。（ig@thm___）\"><figcaption>鄧凱文身材好好。（ig@thm___）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260503/1127661436416561152609352.jpeg/R5TNOf-VHEBFsQIHwiAiCricMvzigEPf9OwpNPTsKTQ\" alt=\"鄧凱文身材好好。（ig@thm___）\"><figcaption>鄧凱文身材好好。（ig@thm___）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260503/1127661438652256256513479.jpeg/7Nd9ubaXnoYqtq32X5dA9hzPoazwqwPGbx0pgm8dKYI\" alt=\"鄧凱文身材好好。（ig@thm___）\"><figcaption>鄧凱文身材好好。（ig@thm___）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260503/1127661440921505792510749.jpeg/whEB-kXO2bO_MQiXO9qN0YwJzWEHjF19l-bXoZfm16E\" alt=\"鄧凱文身材好好。（ig@thm___）\"><figcaption>鄧凱文身材好好。（ig@thm___）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260503/1127661432029057024708293.jpeg/30Ukqe0BP-1132IlW1VGx-qEeAjNp_hbbShsMm0obDI\" alt=\"鄧凱文於《萬千星輝頒獎典禮2025》當晚，喺台下落力為《東張西望》打氣。（ig@thm___）\"><figcaption>鄧凱文於《萬千星輝頒獎典禮2025》當晚，喺台下落力為《東張西望》打氣。（ig@thm___）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260503/1127661434281529344018465.jpeg/a-ntxSi9MtA--3mr0Mtvw5wUocZWrskR_69U__-vVP8\" alt=\"鄧凱文於《萬千星輝頒獎典禮2025》當晚，喺台下落力為《東張西望》打氣。（ig@thm___）\"><figcaption>鄧凱文於《萬千星輝頒獎典禮2025》當晚，喺台下落力為《東張西望》打氣。（ig@thm___）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260503/1127661436617887744708651.jpeg/CVJHMAu2wAQUS6Z90zimeO849DURHPswagzy1GoM8tQ\" alt=\"鄧凱文於《萬千星輝頒獎典禮2025》當晚，喺台下落力為《東張西望》打氣。（ig@thm___）\"><figcaption>鄧凱文於《萬千星輝頒獎典禮2025》當晚，喺台下落力為《東張西望》打氣。（ig@thm___）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260503/1127661438656450560571904.jpeg/l-8lG7YqIsqFSHomA8B_TAf-P6kMNy8A9tp8FPbafBQ\" alt=\"參加《魔音女團》。（ig@thm___）\"><figcaption>參加《魔音女團》。（ig@thm___）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260503/1127661440883757056964705.jpeg/_YL7f-JNiLLEJjrK-9dt9sP-9oWSpZO2Fiw8AxYsPAM\" alt=\"參加《魔音女團》。（ig@thm___）\"><figcaption>參加《魔音女團》。（ig@thm___）</figcaption></figure></body></html>","scraped_at":"2026-05-03T12:10:23.015684+00:00","quality":{"score":3,"chars":1907,"images":49,"source":"HK01 娛樂","fallback":"none"}}